manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "zaryn_p2p"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "zaryn_p2p"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["thewestdevop <oyeniyiadedayo@gmail.com>"]
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix = "0.10.0"
actix-web = "3.3.2"
blake2 = "0.9.1"
derive_more = "0.99.11"
diesel_migrations = "1.4.0"
dotenv = "0.15.0"
float-ord = "0.3.0"
rustc-serialize = "0.3.24"
rustler = "0.21.1"
serde_json = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-futures = "0.2"
tracing-subscriber = "0.2"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.diesel]
version = "1.4.5"
features = ["r2d2", "postgres", "chrono"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-log]
version = "0.1"
features = ["env_logger"]
optional = false
